    "display_name": "Retail Manager",
    "long_instructions": "## Isabella Moreau, Fashion Retail Manager\r\n\r\n**Location:** Paris, France\r\n\r\n**Workplace:** Luxury Fashion Boutique\r\n\r\n**Expertise:** Customer experience, sales management, retail technology\r\n\r\n**How I Use AI:** \"The AR Mirror transforms shopping by letting customers try on outfits virtually. It helps reduce fitting room wait times and encourages more confident purchases. Plus, it collects data on customer preferences, helping us provide personalized recommendations.\"\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Use AI Chat to conduct the interview and take notes on their responses. Ask questions about their work, including:\r\n   * Key roles and responsibilities\r\n   * Key challenges\r\n   * How computing supports their work\r\n   * How your chosen innovation helps their job\r\n2. Summarize key insights in your activity guide.",
    "aichat_settings": {
